<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <meta content="ie=edge" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"/>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,300,400,700,900" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="img/favicon.png" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/navbar.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/footer.css" />
  <title>About Us</title>
 </head>
 <body>
  <% include navbar.ejs %>



  <main class="px-8 py-16">
  <section class="mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Mission</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Our mission is to provide adventurous and exciting tours for people who love to explore the world. We aim to create unforgettable experiences and foster a community of like-minded travelers.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-8">
      <div class="col-span-1 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <img
          alt="Portrait of John Doe, the CEO of Travel"
          class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
          height="300"
          src="https://placehold.co/300x300"
          width="300"
        />


        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">John Doe</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">CEO</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            John is the visionary behind Travel, leading the company with his passion for adventure and exploration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 col-start-3 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <img
          alt="Portrait of Jane Smith, the COO of Travel"
          class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
          height="300"
          src="https://placehold.co/300x300"
          width="300"
        />


        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Jane Smith</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">COO</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Jane ensures that all operations run smoothly, making sure every tour is a success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 col-start-5 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <img
          alt="Portrait of Michael Brown, the CFO of Travel"
          class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
          height="300"
          src="https://placehold.co/300x300"
          width="300"
        />

        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Michael Brown</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">CFO</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Michael manages the financial health of the company, ensuring sustainable growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 col-start-2 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <img
          alt="Portrait of Emily Davis, the Marketing Director of Travel"
          class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
          height="300"
          src="https://placehold.co/300x300"
          width="300"
        />


        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Emily Davis</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Marketing Director</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Emily is the creative force behind our marketing campaigns, spreading the word about our amazing tours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 col-start-4 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <img
          alt="Portrait of David Wilson, the Customer Service Manager of Travel"
          class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
          height="300"
          src="https://placehold.co/300x300"
          width="300"
        />


        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">David Wilson</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Customer Service Manager</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            David ensures that all our customers have a seamless and enjoyable experience from start to finish.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('footer') -%>


  <script>
   document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
                const themeToggle = document.querySelector('.theme-toggle');
                themeToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    document.body.classList.toggle('dark-theme');
                    const icon = themeToggle;
                    if (document.body.classList.contains('dark-theme')) {
                        icon.classList.remove('fa-sun', 'text-yellow-500');
                        icon.classList.add('fa-moon', 'text-blue-500');
                    } else {
                        icon.classList.remove('fa-moon', 'text-blue-500');
                        icon.classList.add('fa-sun', 'text-yellow-500');
                    }
                });
            });
  </script>
 </body>
</html>